---
// Bento 그리드 — 큰 카드 1개 + 작은 카드 2개
---

<section id="features" class="relative bg-base-200 py-24 sm:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6">
    <!-- 섹션 헤더 -->
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <span class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-primary">기능</span>
      <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-base-content sm:text-4xl lg:text-[2.75rem]">
        가계부 쓰는 법이<br />이렇게 달라져요.
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-base-content/60">
        클릭, 선택, 입력 대신 그냥 말하세요. 나머지는 AI가 합니다.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Bento -->
    <div class="mt-14 grid gap-4 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-rows-[auto_auto]">
      <!-- 큰 카드: 자연어 입력 -->
      <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-base-300 bg-base-100 p-8 transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-xl lg:col-span-2 lg:row-span-2 lg:p-10">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary/10 text-primary">
            <svg class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 17a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6.828a2 2 0 0 0-1.414.586l-2.202 2.202A.71.71 0 0 1 2 21.286V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h16a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-primary">자연어 입력</span>
        </div>

        <h3 class="mt-5 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-base-content lg:text-3xl">
          한 문장이면 충분해요
        </h3>
        <p class="mt-3 max-w-lg text-base text-base-content/60">
          금액, 날짜, 카테고리를 일일이 고를 필요 없어요. 평소 말하듯 쓰면 AI가 알아서 정리합니다.
        </p>

        <!-- 입력 → 파싱 예시 3개 -->
        <div class="mt-8 space-y-3">
          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 rounded-2xl border border-base-300 bg-base-200/50 p-4 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:gap-4">
            <div class="flex-1 text-sm font-medium text-base-content/80">"어제 점심 12,000원"</div>
            <svg class="hidden h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-base-content/30 sm:block" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
              <span class="rounded-full bg-secondary/10 px-2.5 py-1 text-[11px] font-semibold text-secondary">🍱 식비</span>
              <span class="rounded-full bg-base-content/5 px-2.5 py-1 text-[11px] font-semibold text-base-content/70">-12,000원</span>
              <span class="rounded-full bg-base-content/5 px-2.5 py-1 text-[11px] font-semibold text-base-content/70">어제</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 rounded-2xl border border-base-300 bg-base-200/50 p-4 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:gap-4">
            <div class="flex-1 text-sm font-medium text-base-content/80">"월급 300만원 들어왔어"</div>
            <svg class="hidden h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-base-content/30 sm:block" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
              <span class="rounded-full bg-success/10 px-2.5 py-1 text-[11px] font-semibold text-success">💼 월급</span>
              <span class="rounded-full bg-base-content/5 px-2.5 py-1 text-[11px] font-semibold text-base-content/70">+3,000,000원</span>
              <span class="rounded-full bg-base-content/5 px-2.5 py-1 text-[11px] font-semibold text-base-content/70">오늘</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col gap-2 rounded-2xl border border-base-300 bg-base-200/50 p-4 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:gap-4">
            <div class="flex-1 text-sm font-medium text-base-content/80">"넷플릭스 구독 결제됨"</div>
            <svg class="hidden h-4 w-4 flex-shrink-0 text-base-content/30 sm:block" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
              <span class="rounded-full bg-info/10 px-2.5 py-1 text-[11px] font-semibold text-info">🎬 구독</span>
              <span class="rounded-full bg-base-content/5 px-2.5 py-1 text-[11px] font-semibold text-base-content/70">-17,000원</span>
              <span class="rounded-full bg-base-content/5 px-2.5 py-1 text-[11px] font-semibold text-base-content/70">오늘</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 작은 카드 1: 자동 리포트 -->
      <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-base-300 bg-base-100 p-7 transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-xl">
        <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-secondary/10 text-secondary">
          <svg class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M3 3v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h16"/><path d="M18 17V9"/><path d="M13 17V5"/><path d="M8 17v-3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-4 text-xl font-bold text-base-content">자동 리포트</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-base-content/60">
          월말에 돌아보지 않아도 AI가 먼저 정리해서 알려줘요.
        </p>

        <!-- 미니 바 차트 -->
        <div class="mt-6 flex items-end gap-2 h-20">
          <div class="w-full rounded-t-md bg-primary/20" style="height: 35%"></div>
          <div class="w-full rounded-t-md bg-primary/40" style="height: 60%"></div>
          <div class="w-full rounded-t-md bg-primary" style="height: 90%"></div>
          <div class="w-full rounded-t-md bg-primary/60" style="height: 70%"></div>
          <div class="w-full rounded-t-md bg-primary/30" style="height: 45%"></div>
          <div class="w-full rounded-t-md bg-primary/50" style="height: 55%"></div>
          <div class="w-full rounded-t-md bg-primary/25" style="height: 30%"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-2 flex justify-between text-[10px] font-medium text-base-content/40">
          <span>월</span><span>화</span><span>수</span><span>목</span><span>금</span><span>토</span><span>일</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 작은 카드 2: 대화형 검색 -->
      <div class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-base-300 bg-base-100 p-7 transition hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-xl">
        <div class="flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-accent/10 text-accent">
          <svg class="h-5 w-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.34-4.34"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-4 text-xl font-bold text-base-content">대화형 검색</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-base-content/60">
          필터 대신 질문하세요. 필요한 답만 돌려드립니다.
        </p>

        <!-- 검색 목업 -->
        <div class="mt-6 space-y-2">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-xl border border-base-300 bg-base-200/50 px-3 py-2.5 text-xs">
            <svg class="h-3.5 w-3.5 text-base-content/40" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><path d="m21 21-4.34-4.34"/></svg>
            <span class="text-base-content/70">이번달 커피값 얼마?</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between rounded-xl bg-primary/5 px-3 py-2.5 text-xs">
            <span class="text-base-content/70">☕ 카페 · 12건</span>
            <span class="font-bold text-primary tabular-nums">47,300원</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
